    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in exceptional, mint condition, essentially indistinguishable from a brand-new model. The exterior paint retains its original showroom shine with absolutely no scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the upholstery and surfaces showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, the car performs flawlessly, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience with all systems functioning perfectly. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in peak aesthetic and mechanical form.",
