    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and structural integrity. Featuring a refined exterior and a well-appointed cabin, it offers a superior driving experience characterized by reliability and poise. This selection represents a premier opportunity for the discerning professional to acquire a high-caliber pre-owned asset that delivers exceptional value without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
